0.	User
•	UserID (int, PK, NN)
•	Name (varchar(50), NN)
•	UserType (enum('Rider', 'Driver'), NN)
0.	Driver
•	DriverID (int, PK, FK, NN)
•	Driver_mode (bool, NN)
•	Rating (float, NN)
0.	Trip
•	TripID (int, PK, NN)
•	RiderID (int, FK, NN)
•	DriverID (int, FK, NN)
•	Pickup_location (varchar(200), NN)
•	Dropoff_location (varchar(200), NN)
•	Fare (decimal(7,2), NN)
0.	Rating
•	RatingID (int, PK, NN)
•	TripID (int, FK, NN)
•	RiderID (int, FK, NN)
•	DriverID (int, FK, NN)
•	Rating_score (int, NN, CHECK (Rating_score BETWEEN 1 AND 5))

Note: PK - Primary Key, NN - Not Null, UQ - Unique, FK - Foreign Key, varchar(N) - Variable Character with N length,
decimal(M, N) - Decimal value with M total digits and N digits after the decimal point, datetime - Date and Time data type,
enum - Enumeration data type, bool - Boolean data type, float - Floating-point number data type.
